    stem: `An 80-year-old woman sustains a fall in the bathroom and is brought to the emergency department by her daughter. She has severe pain and decreased range of motion in all directions in the right hip. The right leg appears shorter than the left and is externally rotated. A bedside portable X-ray of the pelvis is taken which is shown in the following photograph. Which one of the following is the most appropriate management option for this patient?`,
