    topic: "Orthopaedics",
    subtopic: "Walking aid technique",
    stem: `A 72-year-old patient of yours has presented to your clinic for advice regarding osteoarthritis of his right knee. He finds walking difficult due to pain. You recommend that he use a stick as a walking aid. He needs to know how he should use it. Which one of the following is the appropriate recommendation for holding the stick and walking?`,
